{"tid":2328412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"硬過Nokia 3310嘅智能手機終於出現啦!","createTime":"2020-12-16T13:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T14:36:03.000Z","uid":365089,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c4022e657bd5a98c144f5dd5954476d5d8c886","tid":2328412,"uid":365089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:41:54.000Z","msg":"iPhone從200層樓高「墜機」！超晃實拍畫面曝光　神到沒摔壞<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201216/UZSA3C4WAZFU3LUEYKAYVMH2QM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201216%2FUZSA3C4WAZFU3LUEYKAYVMH2QM%2F&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1wpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=caf19752\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201216%2FUZSA3C4WAZFU3LUEYKAYVMH2QM%2F&h=ef13269b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201216/UZSA3C4WAZFU3LUEYKAYVMH2QM/</a><br />\n<br />\n巴西環保主義紀錄片製片人加里歐托(Ernesto Galiotto)，近日搭乘直升機，在里約熱內盧海岸上空拍攝影片，加里歐托在約610公尺的高空，利用iPhone 6s拍攝影片，但沒想到一個手滑，iPhone 6s當場「墜機」。但是「墜機」後的結果令人大驚，加里歐托也順勢公布iPhone 6s在「墜機」期間拍攝到的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n據巴西《G1》報導，日前加里歐托飛到海岸上空拍攝紀錄片，他拿出iPhone 6s並伸出窗戶外拍攝，但可能是高空風速太強，加里歐托一時手滑，手機就直接從高空中墜落下去，當下讓加里歐托和直升機駕駛都非常錯愕。加里歐托原本以為iPhone 6s就此「身亡」，但沒想到發生「奇蹟」。<br />\n<br />\n加里歐托用另一台手機啟動「尋找我的iPhone」後，發現這台 iPhone 6s 掉在沙灘上，沒有掉入水中。原本加里歐托也以為手機應該死在沙灘上了，但沒想到這台 iPhone 6s只有螢幕和機體部分破損，其他功能依舊正常運作，連「墜機」的15秒超晃畫面都拍下來。加里歐托覺得太神奇，於是重新編輯影片後上傳，讓大眾看這難得的「墜機畫面」。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">iPhone 6s瞬間成為軍事設備</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c98225eb576d73ec559bc36b30e0858d09d0613","tid":2328412,"uid":30274,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"如果係3310就已經直接穿入地核啦"},{"pid":"a6dd2369a5671ba6121bc23cd83f4169dfa779d2","tid":2328412,"uid":301050,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c98225eb576d73ec559bc36b30e0858d09d0613","tid":2328412,"uid":30274,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"如果係3310就已經直接穿入地核啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:49:53.000Z","msg":"咁啱想講3310落地地下會有個窿"},{"pid":"a93c671523da2c19c66e0d6f9eddd995cf63bdeb","tid":2328412,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:51:36.000Z","msg":"跌入沙漠？<br />\n沙緩衝左個力？"},{"pid":"d7da84e608c6ab59c5888592a51265ea4e069955","tid":2328412,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:33:48.000Z","msg":"硬過Nokia 3310?<br />\n<br />\n3310咁跌法嘅話人類絕咗種啦"},{"pid":"f90511505c48c5197fb4fd096318b6c129b8b35d","tid":2328412,"uid":365089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c98225eb576d73ec559bc36b30e0858d09d0613","tid":2328412,"uid":30274,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:45:46.000Z","msg":"如果係3310就已經直接穿入地核啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}